sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Sup as Supervisor / Manager
    actor HK as Housekeeping Staff
    participant UI as Rooms Page<br/>(/rooms tab Housekeeping)
    participant SB as Supabase Client
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant CronAPI as /api/housekeeping/<br/>daily-maintenance
    participant ChkAPI as /api/housekeeping/<br/>checkout-cleaning

    Sup->>UI: Buka /rooms, klik tab Housekeeping
    UI->>SB: from('housekeeping_tasks')<br/>.select('*, rooms(...)')
    SB->>DB: SELECT housekeeping_tasks JOIN rooms
    DB-->>SB: tasks[]
    SB-->>UI: data
    UI-->>Sup: Render task list + filter status, priority

    rect rgb(220, 252, 231)
    Note over Sup,DB: CREATE Task Manual
    Sup->>UI: Klik "Add Task"
    Sup->>UI: Isi: roomId, taskType,<br/>priority, assigned_to, notes,<br/>estimated_duration
    UI->>SB: from('housekeeping_tasks').insert({...})
    SB->>DB: INSERT
    DB-->>SB: new task row
    SB-->>UI: data
    UI-->>Sup: Toast "Tugas ditambahkan"
    end

    rect rgb(254, 243, 199)
    Note over CronAPI,DB: CREATE Tasks Otomatis (Daily)
    CronAPI->>SB: rpc('run_daily_housekeeping_tasks')
    SB->>DB: function generates daily<br/>tasks for all occupied rooms
    DB-->>SB: tasks count
    end

    rect rgb(254, 243, 199)
    Note over ChkAPI,DB: CREATE Task Otomatis (Post-Checkout)
    ChkAPI->>SB: from('housekeeping_tasks').insert({<br/>task_type: 'checkout',<br/>room_id: ?,<br/>priority: 'high'<br/>})
    SB->>DB: INSERT
    end

    rect rgb(219, 234, 254)
    Note over HK,DB: UPDATE Task Status
    HK->>UI: Buka /rooms tab Housekeeping<br/>(filter assigned_to = me)
    HK->>UI: Klik task → "Start Task"
    UI->>SB: from('housekeeping_tasks').update({<br/>status: 'in-progress',<br/>started_at: NOW()<br/>}).eq('id', taskId)
    SB->>DB: UPDATE
    DB-->>SB: ok
    UI-->>HK: Status berubah, badge update

    HK->>UI: Selesaikan tugas, klik "Complete"
    UI->>SB: update({<br/>status: 'completed',<br/>completed_at: NOW()<br/>})
    SB->>DB: UPDATE

    alt task_type = 'checkout'
        UI->>SB: from('rooms').update({status: 'available'})<br/>.eq('id', task.room_id)
        SB->>DB: UPDATE
        Note over DB: Kamar siap dijual kembali
    end
    end

    Note over UI: Tidak ada Supabase Realtime<br/>untuk housekeeping_tasks —<br/>list refresh manual atau<br/>navigasi ulang
